63 (<strong>age 59 years; as of 2022<\/strong>) in Mumbai. Her zodiac sign is Virgo.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour:<\/strong>\u00a0Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour:<\/strong> Salt &amp; Pepper<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-114865\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwala-1-156x300.jpg\" alt=\"Rekha Jhunjhunwala\" width=\"212\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwala-1-156x300.jpg 156w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwala-1.jpg 192w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Rekha Jhunjhunwala&#8217;s father&#8217;s name is Purushotam Premraj Gupta.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Husband &amp; Children<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>On 22 February 1987, Rekha Jhunjhunwala got married to <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/rakesh-jhunjhunwala\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rakesh Jhunjhunwala<\/a>, who is known as The Big Bull of Indian stock markets. In 2004, the couple was blessed with a daughter named Nishtha Jhunjhunwala through an IVF procedure. In 2009, the couple had twin sons named Aryaman Jhunjhunwala &amp; Aryaveer Jhunjhunwala.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_114867\" style=\"width: 420px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwala-with-her-husband-and-kids.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-114867\" class=\" wp-image-114867\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwala-with-her-husband-and-kids.jpg\" alt=\"Rekha Jhunjhunwala with her husband and kids\" width=\"410\" height=\"295\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-114867\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rekha Jhunjhunwala with her husband and kids<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Rekha has been working as an investor in the Indian stock markets for a very long time. As of 2022, she is associated with four companies named Jalaram Baba Children\u2019s Nest Education Private Limited, Minosha Digital Solutions Private Limited, Ohm Educom Foundation Private Limited, and Rare Family Foundation. The Rare Family Foundation is a stock brokerage firm started by Rakesh Jhunjhunwala in 1992 using his initials and Rekha&#8217;s initials. (Ra from Rakesh and Re from Rekha).<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_114866\" style=\"width: 865px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-114866\" class=\"wp-image-114866 \" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022-e1660489624583.jpg\" alt=\"Rekha Jhunjhunwala's portfolio as of June 2022\" width=\"855\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022-e1660489624583.jpg 1168w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022-e1660489624583-300x126.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022-e1660489624583-1024x431.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Rekha-Jhunjhunwalas-portfolio-as-of-June-2022-e1660489624583-768x324.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 855px) 100vw, 855px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-114866\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rekha Jhunjhunwala&#8217;s portfolio as of June 2022<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span>Net Worth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In November 2022, with a net worth of Rs 47,650.76 crore (USD 5.9 billion) <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_114862_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_114862_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/profile\/rekha-jhunjhunwala\/?sh=5d5e653a438b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Forbes<\/a><\/span><\/span>, she replaced her husband as the 30th richest person in India. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_114862_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_114862_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_114862_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.moneycontrol.com\/news\/trends\/rekha-jhunjhunwala-replaces-rakesh-jhunjhunwala-on-forbes-india-rich-list-2022-9620131.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Money Control<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Assets_and_Properties\"><\/span>Assets and Properties<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Rekha and her husband collectively own a 4,500 sq ft duplex in South Mumbai\u2019s Malabar Hills that Mr Rakesh bought for Rs 25.25 crore. They also own an 18,000 sq ft holiday home